{{Quote|All right, men, load your weapons.|Mod Terrik to Zeta Squadron|audio=AllRightMenLoadYourWeapons.flac|<ref name="Episode 4">{{Film|IV}}</ref>}}
'''Zeta Squadron''' was one of three [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]] squadrons that made up [[Desert Sands]].

==History==
[[File:Dewback_Patrol.jpg|thumb|left|250px|Members of Zeta Squadron search the desert for R2-D2 and C-3PO.]]
In search of the [[Death Star plans/Legends|Death Star plans]], they were sent to locate the [[Droid/Legends|droids]] [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] and [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. [[Davin Felth/Legends|Davin Felth]] was a member of the squadron under the command of [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Mod Terrik]].

Zeta Squadron destroyed the [[Jawa/Legends|Jawa]] [[Sandcrawler/Legends|sandcrawler]] that collected the two droids and razed the [[Lars homestead/Legends|Lars homestead]]. The Squadron later failed to stop the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']] from escaping [[Docking Bay 94/Legends|Docking Bay 94]]. During that firefight, Terrik was shot from behind by Felth.

